index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF SOCIAL AND HEALTH SERVICES
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Public Health; authorizing an agreement with Washington State Department of Social & Health Services for reimbursement to the City of costs of providing dental services within King County; authorizing an agreement between the City and Neighborhood Health Center of Seattle, Inc. in connection therewith, and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Emergency Fund and declaring an emergency therefor.
